## Stories to implement (in order)

### S01 — Remove duplicate extern in command_registry.cpp

`app/command_registry.cpp` has `api_open_animation_path` declared twice:
- Line 44: `extern void api_open_animation_path(TTestPatternApp&, const std::string&);`
- Line 53-54: same overload repeated

Remove the exact duplicate. Leave the two *distinct* overloads (different signatures) if both are
actually used. Verify with `rg 'api_open_animation_path' app/command_registry.cpp`.
Commit: `fix(api): remove duplicate api_open_animation_path extern — E012 S01`

