### S02 — Register inject_command in capabilities

`inject_command` is handled at `app/command_registry.cpp:435` but is not listed in the
`capabilities` static vector (line 76+). Add a capabilities entry for it so it appears in
`GET /api/capabilities`. Description: "Inject a raw IPC command string for internal testing".
Set `requires_path` to true (it takes a `cmd` param).
Commit: `fix(api): register inject_command in capabilities — E012 S02`

