### S03 — Centralise json_escape

There are three separate JSON escape implementations:
- `app/command_registry.cpp:134` — `json_escape()` (static, local)
- `app/test_pattern_app.cpp` around line 3808 — `TTestPatternApp::jsonEscape()` (member fn)
- Inline escape loops in `app/api_ipc.cpp` paint export and `api_get_state` title escaping

Steps:
1. Promote `json_escape` from `command_registry.cpp` into a new shared header
   `app/core/json_utils.h` as an `inline` function
2. Include it in `command_registry.cpp`, `test_pattern_app.cpp`, `api_ipc.cpp`
3. Remove `TTestPatternApp::jsonEscape` member (update header + all call sites to use `json_escape`)
4. Replace any inline escape loops in `api_ipc.cpp` with the shared function
Commit: `refactor(core): centralise json_escape into app/core/json_utils.h — E012 S03`

